To build the aku library, checkout lapackpp project from CVS, into the same
directory where you have aku project, and first build lapackpp.

In Debian based systems, you need to install the following dependencies:
liblapack-dev
libblas-dev
libfftw3-dev
libsndfile1-dev

In Red Hat based systems, you need to install the following dependencies:
lapack-devel
blas-devel
fftw-devel
libsndfile-devel

In addition, decoder requires swig.
